entry.title: WEATHER ADVISORY , Killarney
entry.summary: Persons in or near this area should be on the lookout for adverse weather conditions and take necessary safety precautions. Issued: 1:31 PM EST Wednesday 04 January 2023

entry.title: Wednesday: Chance of flurries. Temperature steady near zero. POP 40%
entry.summary: Cloudy. 40 percent chance of flurries. Snow mixed with ice pellets beginning late this afternoon. Risk of freezing rain this afternoon. Wind northeast 30 km/h gusting to 50. Temperature steady near zero. Wind chill minus 9 this afternoon. Forecast issued 11:30 AM EST Wednesday 04 January 2023

entry.title: Wednesday night: Snow mixed with ice pellets. Low minus 5.
entry.summary: Snow mixed with ice pellets. Risk of freezing rain this evening. Snow and ice pellet amount 5 to 10 cm. Wind northeast 30 km/h gusting to 50. Low minus 5. Wind chill near minus 12. Forecast issued 11:30 AM EST Wednesday 04 January 2023
